    },
    "We'll promote your content in our app, and we have a referral leaderboard that tracks downloads through your invite link. Climb the list and every new user who opens Onit will see your channel. That's ongoing visibility long after your video goes up!": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We'll promote your content in our app, and we have a referral leaderboard that tracks downloads through your invite link. Climb the list and every new user who opens Onit will see your channel. That's ongoing visibility long after your video goes up!"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nous ferons la promotion de votre contenu dans notre application, et nous avons un classement de parrainage qui suit les téléchargements via votre lien d’invitation. Grimpez dans le classement et chaque nouvel utilisateur qui ouvre Onit verra votre chaîne. C’est une visibilité continue bien après la mise en ligne de votre vidéo !"
          }
        }
      }
    },
